# === SECRET-LEAK GUARDRAILS (added 2026-04-29 after secret-scan block) ===
# Vendor IDE configs that bake plaintext API keys.
# NEVER commit these — keys belong in .env.secrets / wrangler secret put / Keychain.
**/NOIZYBEAST.json
**/gitmind*.json
**/local_*.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/credentials.json
**/secrets.json
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*

# === VENDOR WEBPACK CHUNKS + AUTH CODE (added 2026-04-29 — pre-commit hook noise) ===
# These directories had .js webpack chunks + python auth modules whose variable
# names (variable-name patterns) tripped the pre-commit secret pattern check.
# The patterns are not actual secrets, but rather than tune the hook, we exclude
# the noisy trees. Original empire code lives at /repos/* and openclaw-36/*.
AI-FAMILY/DREAM/code/
NOIZYVOX/code/

# All AI-FAMILY/*/code/ subtrees — vendor JS chunks + code copies trip the
# pre-commit hook on variable-name patterns ("<pwd>=" / "<key>=" / etc).
# Original empire code lives at /repos/* and openclaw-36/* and landing/*.
AI-FAMILY/*/code/

# Brand- and persona-level /code/ subtrees — vendor noise + variable-name false positives
NOIZYFISH/code/
NOIZYKIDZ/code/
NOIZYLAB/code/
THE-AQUARIUM/code/
THE-WISDOM-PROJECT/code/
AI-FAMILY/GABRIEL/code/
AI-FAMILY/ENGR_KEITH/code/
AI-FAMILY/POPS/code/
AI-FAMILY/LUCY/code/
AI-FAMILY/SHIRL/code/
